data.description: If you have been looking for an authentic ranch-style home set on approximately 5.5 acres, and close to town, your search ends here! This four-bedroom home boasts a well-appointed kitchen featuring a large island, granite countertops and upgraded cabinets, complemented by a spacious pantry for ample grocery storage. Brand new roof put on in 2023. The property includes a four-car garage with electricity to accommodate your various vehicles and equipment. This would also make the perfect workshop! Conveniently located just a quick drive away from Warrensburg and Whiteman AFB.
